<title>USA: Covance to join S&amp;P MidCap 400 Index.</title>
<headline>Covance to join S&amp;P MidCap 400 Index.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-01-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Standard &amp; Poor's Corp on Monday said it would add Covance Inc to the S&amp;P MidCap 400 Index after the close of trading on Monday, January 13.</p>
<p>Covance is about to be spun off by Corning Inc.</p>
<p>In order to make room for Covance, A.T. Cross Co. will be transferred to the S&amp;P SmallCap 600 Index. A.T. Cross will replace Merisel Inc in the S&amp;P SmallCap index.</p>
